data.description: Step into your next chapter at this inviting home in Columbia Heights! With 5 bedrooms &3 baths. Your private oasis awaits in the large primary bedroom, complete with a modern 3/4 ensuite bathroom and a spacious walk-in closet. Imagine mornings spent in your sunlit sunroom, conveniently adjacent to the kitchen and dining area. Need room for entertainment? You've got it! Choose from two roomy family areas or opt for a quieter moment in the additional living room. Enjoy the fully fenced yard, all set on a convenient corner lot that puts you within arm's reach of local amenities. Quality is evident with the homes well-maintained roof and siding, which are only about 5 years old, as well as several updated windows & and a newly installed furnace to keep you warm on those chilly Minnesota nights. And here's the cherry on top: the installed solar panels not only significantly reduce your electric bill but may even put some money back in your pocket! New Stainless Steel Appliances
